descriptionHtml:
This is used my new BreakUndies systems that break together with Health.
Can be temper but can equiped only one actor.

[b]Installation:[/b]
Unpack the contents to your Skyrim data folder.

[b]Require:[/b]
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]Skyrim Script Extender (SKSE)[/url]

[b]Recommend:[/b]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26442]Qasmoke Travel Spell[/url]

[b]Obtain:[/b]
Can get all by dialog when game started.
Otherwise, go to Qasmoke(testing hall).
1 - [coc qasmoke] in the console.
2 - Buy it by merchant.
3 - [coc Riverwood] in the console.

[b]Version:[/b]
1.0 - Initial

[b]Special Thanks:[/b]
dimon99 for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709]UNP[/url]
author: anano
